{"tid":827761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好心同人講嘢咪戴耳機","createTime":"2018-09-19T07:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T07:38:45.000Z","uid":204788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f2940fcc08b81b873481209d272b13511b4cacd","tid":827761,"uid":204788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:27:25.000Z","msg":"邊聽歌邊同人講嘢<br />\n又講得細聲<br />\n人哋以為你講電話啊<br />\n尤其是戴Airpods嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頭先喺餐廳裏面<br />\n有條友帶住對Airpods陰聲細氣咁嗌杯檸水<br />\n結果碗嘢食完杯嘢都未嚟<br />\n成鋪冇人知佢嗌過嘢飲<br />\n仲要喺到閪撚晒面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟一路用耳機 一路同人交流嘅人係咩心態<br />\n印象中毒撚先會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ccd1fc4a528efb03e31d2659c20b7504e3291f4","tid":827761,"uid":4308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:31:16.000Z","msg":"助聽器呀"},{"pid":"94931b3648f02c750cbc3431dfe7b1fd9d1b62ca","tid":827761,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:38:45.000Z","msg":"人既問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果真係聽緊歌 應該講得會大聲啲 因為自己聽唔到自己把聲"}]}